  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The activity is oriented to support and promote networking in Bioethics with special atention to UNESCO LAC Bioethics network (Redbioetica UNESCO) in its three most important and relevant accions, the International congress of Redbio&#xE9;tica UNESCO, the webpage and the regional Journal (Revista Redbio&#xE9;tica). It also promote interagency partnership with the Global Summit of NBC and special cooperation with Africa as a result of the agreement between Unesco Offices in Africa and MVD Office and LAC Redbioetica UNESCO. It aims to promote the Recomendatino on Science and scientific researchers.</narrative>
